com.yworks.yfiles.layout

Class ItemCollection<TItem>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.ItemCollection<TItem>
  • Type Parameters:
    TItem - The type of the items in the collection.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DpKeyItemCollection, SingleItemCollection

    public class ItemCollection<TItem>
extends Object
    Provides different ways to define the items in a collection for use with LayoutData.

    Only one of the provided ways to define a collection can be used at the same time, therefore only one of the properties Items, Mapper, and Delegate should be set on each instance.

    This class supports LayoutData implementations and does not usually have to be used explicitly.
